  <brief_title>Cerebrospinal Fluid IL-6, IL-8 and PCT as Early Marker of an Intrathecal Infection in Neurosurgical Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Early Detection of CSF Infection in Neurosurgical Patients</official_title>
